title: The Dan Patrick Show-BEST OF-for Aug 11, 2020

description:
Dan Patrick teases our Emmy's Watch Party tonight, and recaps the College Football news from the past 24 hours. He's joined by SEC Commissioner Greg Sankey and PGA Championship winner Collin Morikawa. Plus, the boys revisit Matt Harvey's infamous Qualcomm interview.
